			<description><![CDATA[<p><span style="font-family: Times; line-height: normal; font-size: medium;"> </span></p>
<div style="color: #000000; font-family: Georgia, Times, serif; font-size: 13px; line-height: 1.5; background-image: initial; background-attachment: initial; background-origin: initial; background-clip: initial; background-color: #ffffff; outline-width: 0px; outline-style: initial; outline-color: initial; background-position: initial initial; background-repeat: initial initial; margin: 8px;">
<p><em>Are you an accomplished web developer with experience of Javascript, AJAX and frameworks like jQuery or ExtJS?</em></p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong><strong>THE ROLE</strong></strong></p>
<p>EngageSciences is looking for a <strong>lead web developer</strong> to join our team and help us build new online applications. You'll get to work with the latest technologies and frameworks like jQuery, Flex and Grails; with cloud-based services such as Amazon EC2; and with social networks like Twitter, Facebook and YouTub  e. You'll take on a key role within our development team - being responsible for implementing the presentation tier of our apps - delivering user interfaces that are both a breeze to use and a joy to behold.</p>
<p>We will provide an excellent compensation package for the right candidate.</p>
<p> </p>
<p><strong><strong>REQUIREMENTS</strong></strong></p>
<p>We think the following skills are key to the role:</p>
<ul>
<li>5+ years building out web front-ends</li>
<li>Deep experience of Javascript, ideally using jQuery and/or ExtJS</li>
<li>Superb understanding of XHTML and CSS</li>
<li>An understanding of testing methods for browser compatibility</li>
<li>Experience working in scripting languages to build out views such as JSP, JSTL or PHP</li>
<li>Comfortable working in a lightweight agile process</li>
<li>Experience or knowledge of view-templating languages like Velocity or GSP</li>
<li>Experience working with Grails is a major plus</li>
</ul>
<p> </p>
<p><strong><strong>ABOUT US</strong></strong></p>
<p>We are a young startup looking to build next-generation online marketing applications. The company's leadership has a strong engineering, design and development background and puts great emphasis on ensuring the development team has the right tools, environment and freedom to do what they do best - build great software.</p>
<ul>
<li>You'll get to be part of building new online services from the ground up, able to influence and part of the core design team.</li>
<li>You'll get to work with modern Java-based frameworks and libraries such as Grails and Groovy.</li>
<li>There'll be opportunities to work on areas such online video streaming, Flex and AIR applications, iPhone applications and machine learning algorithms.</li>
<li>You'll use first-class development tools and environments, the latest Apple equipment, and be based in a great office.</li>
<li>You'll receive a stock plan and equity in the company as part of your package.</li>
</ul>
</div>
